==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Resty
<hw>Rest"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Disposed to rest;
indisposed toexercton; sluggish; also, restive.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Burton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Where the master is too <qex>resty</qex> or too rich to say his
own prayers.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Resubjection</ent>⟦br⟧
